The PubPower Publisher Dashboard Extension provides an easy and efficient way for publishers to access their most recent reports, account information, and account manager details directly from their browser. 

This extension is designed to simplify management and offer real-time insights, ensuring that publishers can stay up to date with their performance metrics and account details without navigating away from their work.

Website: https://pubpower.io
Email: support@pubpower.io
